560
00:46:36,849 --> 00:46:39,217
Oh tidak, tidak.

561
00:46:39,217 --> 00:46:41,188
Aku akan berlibur.

562
00:46:41,188 --> 00:46:43,311
Sekitar 1 bulan.

563
00:46:43,311 --> 00:46:45,349
Aku ingin menenangkan diri.

